en: Throughout the year we welcome you here for a break or holidays at the heart of the Touraine. Nestled on the edge of a small oak grove in the heights of Savonnières, our guest house will appeal to you with its contemporary charm, peace and quiet and woody scents. Situated close to the Loire à Vélo cycling trail, the guest house is a real haven for those who love walking and cycling. Discover the unique natural heritage along the "Royal River" as a couple or with family.
